room_title: Escape room "Detective's Office" by Murder Escape in Tulsa
review: This room was such a blast! Lots of swearing ensued, but it was so much fun. We had 3 people and were able to solve the room.

room_title: Escape room "Detective's Office" by Murder Escape in Tulsa
review: I took my mother and kids and we had a blast. We loved the puzzles. The best part was getting to actually solve a murder. Extremely clever activity!
